member.name: M:Binance.Net.BinanceBrokerageClient.ChangeSubAccountCommissionAsync(System.String,System.Decimal,System.Decimal,System.Nullable{System.Decimal},System.Nullable{System.Decimal},System.Nullable{System.Int32},System.Threading.CancellationToken)
member.summary:
Change Sub Account Commission
You need to enable "trade" option for the api key which requests this endpoint
If margin disabled, it is not allowed to send marginMakerCommission or marginTakerCommission
If margin enabled, marginMakerCommission or marginTakerCommission has default value as spotMakerCommission or spotTakerCommission
member.param: The receive window for which this request is active. When the request takes longer than this to complete the server will reject the request

member.name: M:Binance.Net.BinanceBrokerageClient.ChangeSubAccountFuturesCommissionAdjustmentAsync(System.String,System.String,System.Int32,System.Int32,System.Nullable{System.Int32},System.Threading.CancellationToken)
member.summary:
Change Sub Account Futures Commission Adjustment
You need to enable "trade" option for the api key which requests this endpoint
The sub-account's futures commission of a symbol equals to the base commission of the symbol on the sub-account's fee tier plus the commission adjustment
If futures disabled, it is not allowed to set subaccount's futures commission adjustment on any symbol
member.param: The receive window for which this request is active. When the request takes longer than this to complete the server will reject the request

member.name: M:Binance.Net.BinanceBrokerageClient.GetSubAccountFuturesCommissionAdjustmentAsync(System.String,System.String,System.Nullable{System.Int32},System.Threading.CancellationToken)
member.summary:
Query Sub Account Futures Commission Adjustment
The sub-account's futures commission of a symbol equals to the base commission of the symbol on the sub-account's fee tier plus the commission adjustment
If symbol not sent, commission adjustment of all symbols will be returned
If futures disabled, it is not allowed to set subaccount's futures commission adjustment on any symbol
member.param: The receive window for which this request is active. When the request takes longer than this to complete the server will reject the request

When Fast Withdraw Switch is on, transferring funds to a Binance account will be done instantly. There is no on-chain transaction, no transaction ID and no withdrawal fee.
